1045
01:23:58,664 --> 01:24:00,207
Es neredzēju. Ko tu nopirki?

1046
01:24:00,916 --> 01:24:02,793
Piedod. Aizmirsu tev pastāstīt. Albumu.

1047
01:24:03,335 --> 01:24:04,336
Kuru?

1048
01:24:05,003 --> 01:24:06,380
"<i>The Best of Nina Simone</i>".

1049
01:24:08,423 --> 01:24:10,259
Cerams, paņēmi čeku.

1050
01:24:12,261 --> 01:24:14,847
Domāju, tas ir forši,
